Title: This is the Way the World Ends
Plot: In the season 6 finale, Dexter and Homicide race against a lunar eclipse to catch the Doomsday Killers before their final gruesome act; Debra struggles with a new emotional reality.
GuestStars: Aimee Garcia, Billy Brown, Josh Cooke, Rya Kihlstedt, Evan George Kruntchev, Luke Andrew Kruntchev, Cory Blevins
